{"lemma":"مُظْلِمِي","slug":"مُظْلِمِي","root":"ظ.ل.م","root_slug":"ظ-ل-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ظ-ل-م","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"مُظْلِم","root":"ظلم","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n27663","n27665"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8F%D8%B8%D9%92%D9%84%D9%90%D9%85%D9%90%D9%8A"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"dark, becoming dark (lack of light)"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"black, becoming black (lack of light)"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"intensely dark, intensely black"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"very evil","tags":["figuratively"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of أَظْلَمَ (ʔaẓlama, “to be or become dark”), denominal verb derived from the root ظ ل م (ẓ l m) of ظُلْمَة (ẓulma, “darkness”)."},"ipa":["/muðˤ.lim/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n27663","headword_ar":"مُظْلِمٌ","root":"Zlm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Becoming dark,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: see its verb, 4]. ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEarN muZolimN","text_ar":"شَعَرٌ مُظْلِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Hair intensely black."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nabotN muZolimN","text_ar":"نَبْتٌ مُظْلِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A plant intensely green, inclining to blackness by reason of its"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deep"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"greenness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomN muZolimN","text_ar":"يَوْمٌ مُظْلِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A day of much evil:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a very evil day:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a day in which one finds hardship,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"difficulty."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amorN muZolimN","text_ar":"اَمْرٌ مُظْلِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An affair such that one knows not how to enter upon it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, M, K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amorN miZolaAmN","text_ar":"اَمْرٌ مِظْلَامٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) [or,] accord. to Lh, one says ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomN miZolaAmN","text_ar":"يَوْمٌ مِظْلَامٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a day such that one knows not how to enter upon it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n27665","headword_ar":"مُظَلَّمٌ","root":"Zlm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  A house, or chamber,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"decorated with pictures;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA;) as though the pictures were put therein where they should not be: it is related in a trad. that the Prophet, having been invited to a repast, saw the house, or chamber, to be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muZal~am","text_ar":"مُظَلَّم"},{"kind":"text","text":", and turned away, not entering: (M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"adorned with gilding and silvering;"},{"kind":"text","text":"an explanation disapproved by Az, but pronounced by Z to be correct, from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlZ~alomu","text_ar":"الظَّلْمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying “ the lustre, and brightness, of gold. ” (TA.) ―         -b2-  And (assumed tropical:)  Herbage"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spreading"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"munobav~N","text_ar":"مُنْبَثٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"munobat","text_ar":"مُنْبَت"},{"kind":"text","text":"])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon the ground, not rained upon."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b3-  Also, of birds, (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raxam","text_ar":"رَخَم"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vultur percnopterus"},{"kind":"text","text":"], and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"crows,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ravens."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, M, K. *)"}],"source_refs":["M"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}